data.description:
This gorgeous home is in a lovely neighborhood close to Hwy 87 and I-95!
This 2-story boasts a coffered ceiling in the dining room and vaulted ceilings in the family room with a trey ceiling in the Owner's suite.  The huge eat-in kitchen has brand new LPV flooring and is equipped with all Stainless Steel appliances and an island perfect for family gatherings.  Grab a blanket and cozy up under the electric fireplace for a family movie after dinner!  The Owner's suite has a large bathroom with separate vanities, a walk-in shower and a garden tub. Owner is gifting the Washer/Dryer combo in the upstairs laundry!  Work in the garage doing DIY projects on the worktable or exercising on the gifted workout bench!  Lastly, Enjoy early morning coffee on either of your front or back-covered porches!  There is also plenty of storage inside the home and outside in the Storage shed.  This is a must see!  You will not be disappointed!
Submit all offers to sonyasmith48@gmail.com
